726933f-a.title: Queens: Irving Avenue - Decatur Street
726933f-a.text:
Irving Ave., east from Decatur Street to the Manhattan Beach Branch of the Long Island Railroad. The three story brick building at the right,
is at the N.W. corner of Cooper and Irving Aves.
December 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
